         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">20th June 1879 ¶ My dear Sir. ¶  ¶ I enclose you a Circular from the Italian Government relative to the diseases &amp;c of the Citron family Also an extract from a newspaper and one from a book I lately r...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">79.06.20</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From John Thurston</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M76, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style=""/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation by M: 'Answ 7/8/79'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>20th June 1879</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I enclose you a Circular from the Italian Government relative to the diseases &amp;c of the Citron family Also an extract from a newspaper and one from a book I lately read.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Enclosures not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am quite alarmed at the destruction caused<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>here by one of the "Coccidae".<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>It has only appeared here of late years, but it is ruining every orange and lime tree in the place.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It attacks numerous other plants and I have even found it in the far bush on ferns.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The natives have no name for it, and it was not here when I came to the country<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. Fiji.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in 1865.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Most likely this coccus is the one referred to in the printed extract enclosed and we may have imported it as there described.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Some years ago I remember that in Mauritius they suffered from a parasite to which the local name of "pou blanc" was given but a "pou rouge"<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>white louse; red louse.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was introduced which ate up its white brother and at same time did no harm.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>If with your great knowledge of plant life you could give me any advice on this point I should be greatly obliged.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It appears to me that the use of "Kerosene or linseed oil" even if effective could never be carried out to any extent and I am anxious to know whether the insect has a "natural enemy" in Australia that could be imported.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am preparing a set of Ferns which I hope to send you shortly.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Believe me</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Very faithfully yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Jno B Thurston.</p>
         </div>
